---
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import SeoMeta from '~/components/common/SeoMeta.astro';
---

<SeoMeta 
  title="Winning with SalesTag — Sales Playbooks"
  description="Tactical guides for real-world field reps using the SalesTag system. Learn field sales blueprints, objection handling, daily review rituals, and vault-first mentality."
/>

<PageLayout>
  <main class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Winning with SalesTag</h1>
    
    <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-gray-600">
      Tactical guides for real-world field reps using the SalesTag system. These playbooks combine proven sales techniques with AI-powered insights to maximize your conversion rates.
    </p>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Field Sales Blueprint</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Covers the ideal door-to-door or in-home pitch flow using the SalesTag badge, from intro to close. Learn how to leverage real-time conversation analysis to adapt your approach and build trust with prospects.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Objection Handling Matrix</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        A guide to real-time tags and best practices when facing pricing, spouse, or trust objections. Use SalesTag's AI insights to identify objection patterns and respond with proven counter-strategies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Daily Review Ritual</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        How reps and coaches can use tagged calls every evening to course-correct, improve close rate, and track growth. Transform your recorded conversations into actionable coaching sessions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Vault-First Mentality</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Encourages reps to treat every pitch as a contribution to the Vault — emphasizing clarity, ethics, and confidence. Build valuable conversation data while maintaining the highest standards of professionalism.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</PageLayout> 